{%- comment -%}
  Tier 2 — Family keyword fallback. When the exact hex lookup misses,
  scan the finish name for the most reliable base-metal/color word and
  pick a representative hex for that family. Order matters: more
  visually-dominant words (black, white, pewter) win over secondary
  modifiers (e.g., "Pewter w/ Bronze Wash" stays pewter, not bronze).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if hex == '' -%}
  {%- if normalized contains 'black' -%}{%- assign hex = '#1c1c1a' -%}
